data.description: Welcome to the beautiful 1,600-acre golf course Gated community at Villa D'Este  of The villages at Cypress Creek. Each village surrounds the semi-private golf course and 640-acre nature preserve. This beautiful immaculate 2021 built home consists of a 3 car garage, 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, open floor plan, with formal dining room, livingroom, eat in kitchen space and inside laundry room. The laundry room comes with front loader washer and dryer. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances,  upgraded with granite counter top, and tiled backsplash. The living room and dining room have the latest desirable,beautiful, custom, modern wood accent walls and built in electric fire place.  Enjoy the benefits of a community pool and golf course with No CDD and Low HOA! Not to forget the location is ideal, within a short distance to the interstates, shopping, medical centers and beaches.
